sequenceDiagram
    participant MLApp as ML Application
    participant PyServer as Python Feature Server<br/>:6566/TCP HTTP TLS
    participant GoServer as Go Feature Server<br/>:8080/TCP HTTP/gRPC TLS
    participant Registry as Feature Registry<br/>:6570/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant RegistryREST as Registry REST API<br/>:8080/TCP HTTP TLS
    participant OnlineStore as Online Store<br/>(Redis :6379 / Postgres :5432 / DynamoDB :443)
    participant OfflineStore as Offline Store<br/>(BigQuery / Snowflake :443)
    participant GitRepo as Git Repository<br/>:443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Operator as feast-operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>:6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Notebook as Kubeflow Notebook

    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        Note over MLApp, OnlineStore: Flow 1: Online Feature Retrieval
        MLApp->>PyServer: POST /get-online-features<br/>Auth: OIDC JWT / K8s SA Token
        PyServer->>Registry: Fetch feature metadata<br/>gRPC :6570 / HTTP :8080<br/>Auth: Bearer JWT (intra-comm)
        Registry-->>PyServer: Feature definitions & permissions
        PyServer->>OnlineStore: Read feature values<br/>Redis :6379 (Password) /<br/>Postgres :5432 (User/Pass, SSL) /<br/>DynamoDB :443 (AWS IAM)
        OnlineStore-->>PyServer: Feature values
        PyServer-->>MLApp: JSON response (features)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        Note over GitRepo, OnlineStore: Flow 2: Feature Materialization (CronJob)
        Note right of Operator: CronJob scheduled by operator
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create CronJob
        activate K8sAPI
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: CronJob created
        deactivate K8sAPI
        Note over GitRepo: CronJob Pod executes:
        GitRepo->>GitRepo: Clone feature repo<br/>HTTPS :443 / SSH :22<br/>Auth: Token / SSH key
        GitRepo->>Registry: Fetch feature definitions<br/>gRPC :6570<br/>Auth: Bearer JWT
        Registry-->>GitRepo: Feature definitions
        GitRepo->>OfflineStore: Read historical features<br/>HTTPS :443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Credentials
        OfflineStore-->>GitRepo: Historical feature data
        GitRepo->>OnlineStore: Write materialized features<br/>TLS (configurable)<br/>Auth: Password / certs
    end

    rect rgb(220, 255, 220)
        Note over Operator, Notebook: Flow 3: Notebook Integration (OpenDataHub)
        Notebook->>K8sAPI: Notebook created with label<br/>opendatahub.io/feast-integration=true
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch event (Notebook CR)
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap<br/>{notebook}-feast-config
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: ConfigMap created
        Notebook->>PyServer: POST /get-online-features<br/>via ConfigMap-provided endpoint<br/>:6566/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Auth: OIDC / K8s token
        PyServer-->>Notebook: Feature values
    end

    rect rgb(255, 220, 255)
        Note over Operator, K8sAPI: Flow 4: Auto-Access RBAC Reconciliation
        Operator->>RegistryREST: GET /api/v1/permissions?project={project}<br/>HTTP/HTTPS :8080<br/>Auth: Bearer JWT (intra-comm)
        RegistryREST-->>Operator: Permissions list
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update ClusterRoles<br/>& RoleBindings<br/>HTTPS :6443<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: RBAC resources created
    end
